=====================[ PAYING BY CHEQUE IN THE USA ]==========================

Only Episode 1, INTO THE STORM, is available as Shareware. Register now and
you will receive two more episodes, WHIRLPOOL OF DEATH and HEART OF THE FIRE,
each with different background graphics and enemy craft, giving a massive 75
levels of high-speed arcade action.

The registration fee for AstroFire is $29.95 (US dollars).
This includes all packing and postage costs to anywhere in the world.
Cheques MUST be in US dollars and MUST be drawn on a US bank.

The game will ONLY be supplied on a 720K 3.5" disk.

Make your cheque payable to "PsL (Public software Library)" and send, together
with your completed order form, to:

